- `company` — employer overview, mission, "about us", history, size
- `team` — specific team / org unit, product area, reporting line, scope
- `role` — day-to-day responsibilities, "what you'll do", project context
- `requirements` — must-have qualifications, skills, years, degrees
- `preferred` — nice-to-haves, "bonus points", extra credit
- `benefits` — perks, PTO, compensation prose, remote/visa policy, retirement, healthcare
- `application` — how to apply, interview process, deadlines, relocation, hiring contact
